old men in shops tinkering with their cuckoo clocks.

354
00:29:26,170 --> 00:29:29,000
要不是他们发现了她的尸体 那么她就要到那时候才会
And if they hadn't found her, that's when she'd have come down,

355
00:29:29,090 --> 00:29:31,460
