with all the rock and debris.

356
00:29:31,550 --> 00:29:33,630
那时候我们早就死了多少年了
We'll be long dead by then.

357
00:29:38,760 --> 00:29:40,760
哦
Oh.

358
00:29:41,930 --> 00:29:43,140
把书收起来
Put your book away.

359
