I'm not. I'm just taking an evening course, just for the fun of it.

370
00:30:14,090 --> 00:30:15,170
不是什么了不得的事
It's nothing grand.

371
00:30:15,260 --> 00:30:17,760
- 但没准会有点成就  - 也可能不会有
