I don't think... I don't think Geoff wanted to go to the pub.

383
00:30:49,710 --> 00:30:51,710
他要么去酒吧 要么就得和我们一起购物
It's either that or he comes shopping with us.

384
00:30:51,800 --> 00:30:53,460
