All right, it was a little bit funny.

546
00:43:36,640 --> 00:43:38,180
哦 对不起
Oh, I'm sorry.

547
00:43:38,270 --> 00:43:40,100
我不应该提起这回事的
I shouldn't have brought it up.

548
00:43:40,190 --> 00:43:42,560
你知道杰夫是什么样子
You know what Geoff's like.

549
00:43:42,650 --> 00:43:45,230
他对有些事情太过狂热了
He gets over-passionate about things.

550
00:43:46,190 --> 00:43:48,780
我想这就是你爱上他的原因
I suppose that's why you fell in love with him.

551
00:43:50,740 --> 00:43:52,820
是啊
Yes.

552
00:44:03,710 --> 00:44:06,000
哦 还有另外一件事
Oh, er, there's another thing.

553
00:44:06,090 --> 00:44:07,550
什么？
What?

554
00:44:07,630 --> 00:44:11,090
杰夫说他不确定他会想去工作午餐
Geoff says he's not sure that he wants to go to the works lunch.

555
00:44:11,180 --> 00:44:12,430
克劳利家的吗？
At Crawley's?

556
00:44:12,510 --> 00:44:14,220
- 可就在明天了  - 我知道
- But it's tomorrow.  - I know.

557
00:44:14,310 --> 00:44:15,850
而且这次聚会很早就开始准备了
And it's been organised for so long.

558
00:44:15,930 --> 00:44:19,020
乔治还期待着要把老朋友们都叫到一起来 但如果…
George was looking forward to getting the old gang together but if...

559
00:44:19,100 --> 00:44:20,640
那他说为什么了吗？
Well, did he say why?

560
00:44:20,730 --> 00:44:22,810
